addr="axt-0053">Pataraia's Lemma</fr:link> holds (for <fr:tex>( \mathcal {U} \sqcup \mathcal {V} ^+,  \mathcal {V} ,  \mathcal {V} )</fr:tex>-dcpos)
  then <fr:link
href="axt-003N.xml"
